    {
        "content": "<p>How will this work with ballots? If the submitter's intent was to vote affirmative, and now it becomes a change request, will the submitter then have to withdraw a newly created negative?</p>",
        "id": 190780169,
        "sender_full_name": "Vassil Peytchev",
